{"id":648547,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":2,"day":24}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"184","ytitle":"","mtitle":"黄山松赞","ftitle":"","authors":["金谷"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒲团松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风暴雨，你有宁折不弯的腰身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪压冰封，你有凌霜傲雪的坚贞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可为什么你有这般奇异的树冠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似个松软的蒲团、松软而齐整?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我懂了:为了登攀者的小憩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你才甘愿作出这样的牺牲!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪客松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为攀登者遮阳、挡雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与胆怯者谈心、鼓劲——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你苍翠茂密的绿荫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你热烈而深沉的涛音……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，大山的主人，绿色的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的斗志、你的精神与山川共存!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1983\\02\\832O030701.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>黄山团结松　王珺摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>王珺</FONT>"}]}